---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "10 May 2026";

const sections = [
  {
    title: "1. Who We Are",
    content: [
      "This Privacy Policy applies to Daniel Gierach, operating as a licensed real estate agent under Ray White Bulimba (ABN available on request), located in Brisbane, Queensland, Australia.",
      "We are committed to protecting your personal information in accordance with the Privacy Act 1988 (Cth) and the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs).",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "2. What Personal Information We Collect",
    content: [
      "We may collect the following types of personal information:",
      "- Your full name, email address, phone number and postal address\n- Property address and details relevant to a sale or appraisal\n- Financial information where relevant to a property transaction\n- Any other information you voluntarily provide when contacting us",
      "We only collect personal information that is necessary for the purposes described in this policy.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "3. How We Collect Your Information",
    content: [
      "We collect personal information in the following ways:",
      "- Directly from you when you complete a contact or appraisal request form on this website\n- When you call, email or otherwise communicate with us\n- Through Ray White's digital platforms and property management systems\n- Via third-party property listing platforms such as realestate.com.au or Domain",
      "We do not collect sensitive information (such as health or financial details) unless specifically required and consented to.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "4. Why We Collect Your Information",
    content: [
      "Your personal information is collected and used to:",
      "- Respond to enquiries and provide property appraisals\n- Manage the sale or purchase of a property on your behalf\n- Communicate updates relevant to your property campaign\n- Comply with legal and regulatory obligations under Queensland and Australian law\n- Improve the services we provide",
      "We will not use your information for any purpose that you would not reasonably expect.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "5. Disclosure of Your Information",
    content: [
      "We may share your personal information with:",
      "- Ray White Bulimba and its affiliated offices where necessary to deliver our services\n- Third-party service providers such as marketing platforms, photographers and conveyancers, under confidentiality obligations\n- Property listing platforms (e.g. realestate.com.au, Domain) as required to market your property\n- Government bodies, courts or regulators where required by law",
      "We do not sell, rent or trade your personal information to third parties for marketing purposes.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "6. Direct Marketing",
    content: [
      "With your consent, we may contact you with relevant property market updates, listings or information we believe may be of interest to you.",
      "You may opt out of marketing communications at any time by contacting us directly or using the unsubscribe link in any email we send.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "7. Security of Your Information",
    content: [
      "We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from misuse, interference, loss, and unauthorised access, modification or disclosure.",
      "This includes secure systems through Ray White's platforms and limiting access to your information to those who need it to carry out their duties.",
      "While we take reasonable precautions, no data transmission over the internet is completely secure and we cannot guarantee absolute security.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "8. Accessing and Correcting Your Information",
    content: [
      "You have the right to request access to the personal information we hold about you, and to request corrections if that information is inaccurate, incomplete or out of date.",
      "To make a request, please contact us using the details below. We will respond within a reasonable timeframe and in accordance with the APPs.",
      "In some circumstances we may be required or permitted by law to deny access to certain information.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "9. Cookies and Website Analytics",
    content: [
      "This website may use cookies and analytics tools to understand how visitors use the site. This information is aggregated and does not personally identify you.",
      "You can disable cookies through your browser settings, though this may affect some website functionality.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "10. Tracking and Analytics Tools",
    content: [
      "In line with Australian Privacy Principle 1.4, we name the specific third-party tools that may collect information when you use this website:",
      "Google Analytics 4 (GA4): measures aggregated, anonymised page views, time on page, traffic sources, and basic device data so we can understand which pages are useful. GA4 does not collect names, phone numbers or email addresses. You can opt out by installing the Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on at tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout.",
      "Meta (Facebook) Pixel: tracks page views and form submissions to measure the performance of Facebook and Instagram advertising. The Pixel sets cookies that may be linked to your Meta account if you are logged in. You can opt out via your Meta ad preferences at facebook.com/adpreferences and instagram.com/accounts/privacy_and_security.",
      "Formspree: processes contact, appraisal and walk-through form submissions on our behalf. When you submit a form, the data you enter (name, email, phone, message and any property details) is transmitted to Formspree's servers in the United States and forwarded to Daniel by email. See formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy for their privacy practices.",
      "Google Maps and Places (address autocomplete): used on the property worth, walk-through and landing-page forms to help you select a verified address. Google receives the partial address you type so it can return suggestions. See policies.google.com/privacy for Google's privacy practices.",
      "You can also block these tools at the browser level by enabling tracking protection (built into Safari, Firefox and Brave) or by installing a content blocker such as uBlock Origin.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "11. Links to Third-Party Websites",
    content: [
      "This website may contain links to external websites including Ray White's platforms and property listing portals. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to review their privacy policies independently.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "12. Complaints",
    content: [
      "If you believe we have breached the Australian Privacy Principles or handled your personal information inappropriately, please contact us in the first instance so we can attempt to resolve your concern.",
      "If you are not satisfied with our response, you may lodge a complaint with the Office of the Australian Information Commissioner (OAIC) at www.oaic.gov.au.",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "13. Changes to This Policy",
    content: [
      "We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or applicable law. The current version will always be available on this page with the date of last update noted above.",
    ],
  },
];
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Daniel Gierach Property" description="Privacy Policy for Daniel Gierach Property, compliant with the Australian Privacy Act 1988 and Australian Privacy Principles." draft={true}>


<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════
     HERO
════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:#f2ead4;padding:8rem 0 5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(25,24,23,0.08);">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12">
    <span style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#6b4610;display:block;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Legal</span>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.5rem);font-weight:400;color:#191817;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1rem;">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p style="font-size:0.85rem;color:rgba(25,24,23,0.6);letter-spacing:0.06em;">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════
     INTRO
════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base);padding:4rem 0 2rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.08);">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12">
    <div style="max-width:72ch;">
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.05rem;color:#191817;line-height:1.8;">
        This Privacy Policy explains how Daniel Gierach collects, uses, stores and discloses your personal information. We respect your privacy and are committed to handling your information responsibly and in accordance with Australian law.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════
     POLICY SECTIONS
════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base);padding:2rem 0 6rem;">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-8 lg:px-12">
    <div style="max-width:72ch;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;">

      {sections.map((s) => (
        <div style="padding:2.5rem 0;border-top:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.1);">
          <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:400;color:#191817;margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.3;">{s.title}</h2>
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.75rem;">
            {s.content.map((para) => (
              <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#44403c;line-height:1.9;white-space:pre-line;">{para}</p>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}

      <!-- Contact -->
      <div style="padding:2.5rem 0;border-top:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.1);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.1);">
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:400;color:#191817;margin-bottom:1rem;">14. Contact Us</h2>
        <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:#44403c;line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
          For any privacy-related enquiries, access requests or complaints, please contact:
        </p>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.4rem;padding:1.5rem;background:rgba(185,130,41,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(185,130,41,0.2);">
          <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:700;color:#191817;">Daniel Gierach</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#44403c;">Ray White Bulimba</p>
          <a href="tel:+61412523821" style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#b98229;text-decoration:none;transition:opacity 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.opacity='0.7'" onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'">0412 523 821</a>
          <a href="mailto:daniel.gierach@raywhite.com" style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#b98229;text-decoration:none;transition:opacity 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.opacity='0.7'" onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'">daniel.gierach@raywhite.com</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
